    "Event:311199624": {
        "__typename": "Event",
        "id": "311199624",
        "title": "Discussion: The AI Effect - Does AI Really Make You Productive?",
        "eventUrl": "https://www.meetup.com/pyrvausergroup/events/311199624/",
        "description": "There's no doubt that AI has taken off at an incredible rate. Everywhere you go, AI is there to help. It's on our devices, it's answering our calls, it's even searching the web for us. But is it actually making us more productive?\n\nJoin us for an open discussion on the merits of AI. Where it excels and where it might fall short.\n\n**Schedule**\n5:45 pm - Doors Open / Social\n6:30 pm - Meeting Start\n7:30 pm - Wrap-up\n8:00 pm - Prologue (Social in Scotts Addition)\n\n**All events are open to all skill levels**. If you're just starting out, come to learn and feel free to ask questions. That's where the real learning happens. If you're a more seasoned developer, we'd love to learn from you. Despite what the Zen of Python says, there are usually more than one way to do something, so share your knowledge!\n\n**Free parking** is available in the surface level parking lots on either side of the Ippon building.\n\nJoin our Discord server! **https://pyrva.org/discord**\nWant to sponsor PyRVA? **https://pyrva.org/donate**\nWant to present? **https://forms.gle/q8w3xziArWjud5f67**",
        "aeoDescription": "In-person Python community meetup for PyRVA; open to all skill levels; outcome: attendees learn Python concepts through Q&A and knowledge sharing.",
        "isSaved": false,
